24 SECTION 3. AMENDMENT. Section 54-44.5-09 of the North Dakota Century Code is
25 amended and reenacted as follows:
26 54-44.5-09. Office of renewable energy and energy efficiency.
27 The office of renewable energy and energy efficiency is established within the division of
28 community services. The office shall assist in the development of renewable energy within this
29 state to provide secure, diverse, sustainable, and competitive renewable energy supplies and
30 promote the conservation of energy and the wise use of energy resources in both the public and
31 private sectors. The office shall communicate and disseminate information concerning state and
